OL,3,CControversial hate crime law comes
OL,4,Cinto effect
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government's
OL,7,Fcontroversial new hate crime law came
OL,8,Finto effect on Monday.
OL,10,FThe Hate Crime and Public Order
OL,11,F(Scotland) Act was passed by MSPs in
OL,12,F2021, consolidating existing hate
OL,13,Fcrime legislation and creating a new
OL,14,Foffence of stirring up hatred against
OL,15,Fprotected characteristics, although
OL,16,Fsex has been omitted in favour of a
OL,17,Fstandalone Bill designed to tackle
OL,18,Fmisogyny.
