OL,7,Frace has been on the statute book in
OL,8,FScotland since 1986.
OL,10,FBut the legislation has raised
OL,11,Fconcerns about a potential chilling of
OL,12,Ffree speech.
OL,14,FProminent critics include author JK
OL,15,FRowling, podcaster Joe Rogan and Elon
OL,16,FMusk, the owner of X ` formerly
OL,17,FTwitter.
