OL,6,FIn a letter to Holyrood's Justice
OL,7,FCommittee, they said the law could be
OL,8,F"weaponised" by an "activist fringe"
OL,9,Facross the political spectrum.
OL,11,FBut on Friday, First Minister Humza
OL,12,FYousaf told the PA news agency: "I
OL,13,Fwould say to anybody who thinks they
OL,14,Fare a victim of hatred, we take that
OL,15,Fseriously, if you felt you are a
OL,16,Fvictim of hatred, then of course
OL,17,Freporting that to police is the right
OL,18,Fthing to do.
