OL,3,CControversial hate crime law comes
OL,4,Cinto effect
OL,6,FThe legislation, which he shepherded
OL,7,Fthrough Holyrood as former first
OL,8,Fminister Nicola Sturgeon's justice
OL,9,Fsecretary, "got the right balance"
OL,10,Fbetween protections against hate crime
OL,11,Fand freedom of speech, he said.
OL,13,F"Ultimately, once the Act comes into
OL,14,Fforce, I think it will do exactly what
OL,15,Fwe expect it to do, which is protect
OL,16,Fthe most marginalised in our
OL,17,Fcommunity," he added.
