OL,3,CControversial hate crime law comes
OL,4,Cinto effect
OL,6,FThe Act has been a running sore for
OL,7,Fthe SNP-led Government in recent
OL,8,Fyears, with a number of changes having
OL,9,Fto be made before it was passed and
OL,10,Fthe three-year gap before it came into
OL,11,Feffect.
OL,13,FBut critics, many of whom, including
OL,14,Fthe Harry Potter author, hold gender
OL,15,Fcritical views, have said it would be
OL,16,Fweaponised against them.
OL,18,FSNP MP Joanna Cherry has previously
OL,19,Fsaid being under police investigation
OL,20,Fcould be a punishment in itself.
