OL,3,CControversial hate crime law comes
OL,4,Cinto effect
OL,6,FScottish Tory justice spokesman
OL,7,FRussell Findlay ` who along with his
OL,8,Fparty has been an ardent opponent of
OL,9,Fthe law ` said: "Officers would rather
OL,10,Ftackle real crimes and keep
OL,11,Fcommunities safe, rather than having
OL,12,Fto investigate malicious and spurious
OL,13,Fcomplaints.
OL,15,F"Humza Yousaf should bin his Hate
OL,16,FCrime Act and instead divert resources
OL,17,Ftowards frontline policing which is at
OL,18,Fbreaking point."
