OL,6,FMr Fraser, in a letter last week,
OL,7,Furged the force to delete the file `
OL,8,Fwhich is recorded when an incident
OL,9,Fdoes not meet the hate crime threshold
OL,10,F` and did not rule out legal action if
OL,11,Fhis request was refused.
OL,13,FMr Findlay described Mr Fraser's case
OL,14,Fas "sinister and unacceptable",
OL,15,Fraising concerns "innocent people will
OL,16,Fend up in secret police files".
